] text-text-muted dark:text-gray-500\">Cebu City, PH</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col h-full\">\n<div class=\"flex text-yellow-400 mb-3 text-sm\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined fill-current text-lg\">star</span>\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined fill-current text-lg\">star</span>\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined fill-current text-lg\">star</span>\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined fill-current text-lg\">star</span>\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined fill-current text-lg\">star</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"text-sm text-text-main dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 flex-grow italic\">\"The community support is amazing. Whenever I get stuck on a campaign, the mentors help me out. It feels like having a senior expert.\"</p>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-auto\">\n<div class=\"size-10 rounded-full bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 bg-cover bg-center\" data-alt=\"Portrait of Anna R.\" style='background-image: url(\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCKGgxrOwP1yZ_kH-RoTIg3EBOFAdF9XwlZl3y-wclxeJkAc9zJu6Pa1zL9ie1lRgrrkH4xGu5bLvE1zJoM7J2Cyt1umWkrk4KmKzOeRSQtBJIvHTyLgohjSuGSFv-0ZW1oNjMRKRYVWRc7Otsk_InEkvRJuht_HgJSS5jR9UywuVbEyGD3cohd-1wUDPf_hp--ThoJYIg0Q-NJ9G_2i8icZEsAka5rC9HjXmi-BdGD-wLVS1gxA48LcHfI5b7hjNrp9EA4Hw3UgTjD\");'></div>\n<div>\n<h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-text-main dark:text-white\">Anna R.</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[10px] text-text-muted dark:text-gray-500\">Manila, PH</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"w-full py-12 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark mb-16\">\n<div class=\"px-4 mx-auto max-w-4xl\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary rounded-2xl p-6 text-center text-white shadow-2xl shadow-primary/30 relative overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image: radial-gradient(#ffffff 